gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 120, Cavaliers 113
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Cavaliers, 120-113.  Jayson Tatum (25 points, 10 rebounds, five assists) and Jaylen Brown (25 points, 10-17 FG, four assists) combine for 50 for the Celtics in the victory, while Donovan Mitchell tallied a game-high 29 points and five 3PM for the Cavaliers in the losing effort.  The Celtics improve to 17-5 on the season, while the Cavaliers fall to 13-11.
